  - text: Hello!? Is somebody here? Can anyone hear me?
    portrait: {fileID: 4655753375831476683, guid: 228f1279effd3fe4c9f25f48633bd95a, type: 3}
    speakerName: 
    isRightSide: 0
    showOnTop: 1
    isThought: 0
    forceReopen: 0
    customVoiceSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8df580135e547434a974d209e08152fd, type: 3}
    portraitAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    interactableSpriteChange: {fileID: 0}
    interactableSpriteChangeSound: {fileID: 0}
    owner: {fileID: 0}
    isEndNode: 0
    delayBeforeLine: 3
    autoAdvanceTime: 0
    setNextInteractionVersion: -1
    jumpToLineIndex: -1
    choices: []
    onLineReached:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - text: What's happening? I don't remember when or even how I arrived here... and
      I'm pretty sure that this is not where I'm supposed to be.
    portrait: {fileID: -2007922728593303437, guid: bb1aebbbfea168f4bbccf248000ac714, type: 3}
    speakerName: 
    isRightSide: 0
    showOnTop: 1
    isThought: 0
    forceReopen: 0
    customVoiceSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8df580135e547434a974d209e08152fd, type: 3}
    portraitAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    interactableSpriteChange: {fileID: 0}
    interactableSpriteChangeSound: {fileID: 0}
    owner: {fileID: 0}
    isEndNode: 0
    delayBeforeLine: 3
    autoAdvanceTime: 0
    setNextInteractionVersion: -1
    jumpToLineIndex: -1
    choices: []
    onLineReached:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - text: Maybe this is a dream? Specifically a nightmare?
    portrait: {fileID: -8011202738254376441, guid: 15d7c85b58358194d98a00aab6dff57b, type: 3}
    speakerName: 
    isRightSide: 0
    showOnTop: 1
    isThought: 0
    forceReopen: 0
    customVoiceSound: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 8df580135e547434a974d209e08152fd, type: 3}
    portraitAnimator: {fileID: 0}
    interactableSpriteChange: {fileID: 0}
    interactableSpriteChangeSound: {fileID: 0}
    owner: {fileID: 0}
    isEndNode: 0
    delayBeforeLine: 0
    autoAdvanceTime: 0
    setNextInteractionVersion: -1
    jumpToLineIndex: -1
    choices: []
    onLineReached:
      m_PersistentCalls:
        m_Calls: []
  - text: Whatever it is, I think it is a good idea to start exploring the zone.
      I must remain optimistic.
    portrait: {fileID: -6513743853152151312, guid: bb65c4dcc67f58b4f807620697aadf77, type: 3}
    speakerName: 
    isRightSide: 0
    showOnTop: 1
